==MLL award winners==

Most Valuable Player
* Greg Cattrano: 2002
* Gary Gait: 2005
* Lyle Thompson: 2019

Rookie of the Year
* Brodie Merrill: 2005
* Matt Ward: 2006
* Josh Byrne: 2017

Defensive Player of the Year
* Rob Doerr: 2001

Offensive Player of the Year
* Mark Millon: 2002, 2003
* Lyle Thompson: 2019

Goalie of the Year
* Greg Cattrano: 2001, 2002
* Niko Amato: 2018

Most Improved Player
* Peet Poillon: 2010

