==Recognition==
===Kirby Awards===

1986
* Best Black-and-White Comic: &quot;Love and Rockets&quot;, by Jaime Hernandez and Gilbert Hernandez

Note: In 1988, the Kirby Awards was disbanded and replaced by the Harvey and the Eisner Awards.

